thread.title: Pat Harkin
thread.title_full: Rentokil Pest Control Ireland reviewed by Pat Harkin

author: Pat Harkin
title: Pat Harkin
text:
As we are a very busy Centra convenience store in Naas we operate to the highest standards of hygiene and food safety and I have to say the standard of service and attention when needed is second to none.
We deal with your engineer Thomas and find him to be excellent and a great help to our business.
